<note style="-uslm-lc:I87" topic="definitions" id="id90037355-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Definition</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For definition of “Secretary” as used in this section, see <ref href="/us/pl/117/81/s5002">section 5002 of Pub. L. 117–81</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s263c">section 263c of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
